Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.47,0:01:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:31.50,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1000)}{\pos(320,320)}紡紗曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不明白是不是看錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥怎麼可能會在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 跟你說這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 剛才的話對大家可以保密嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶消失不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經把思念波傳給元老院了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是遇到銀的妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓧塚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去讓這傢伙安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間內隨你怎麼鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是隨我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 怎樣都可以 隨你喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德國 德國
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待妳的禮物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去德國的哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漢堡 不來梅 柏林 慕尼黑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德國什麼最有名來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:03:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽車？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球不是很厲害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底是去看什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥本連茲國防技術博物館
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那方面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算工資不多 也要去玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有好好的幹事務所的活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹭蹭 得累 蹭得累 蹭蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上那個很吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反覆要播好多次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是町長命令嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的狗一直都在對著叫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽抱怨是蒼的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 今天去嗎？卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去 去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那曲子記得了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麥克風
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹭蹭 得累 蹭得累 蹭蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是唱這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快要記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起悠閒的來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 去 才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？練習對手？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 難得的休息日被叫去做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓恭助來做不就可以了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合同裡可是有這款的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦 那就明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我漲工資啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一(eins) 二(zwei) 三(drei) (德語 怨念)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像話 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像話 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒資格說！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是些不像話的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『棒』
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『球球球』
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『壁』
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉和姬勢均力敵呢	
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 她癡迷武器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『彈彈彈彈…』
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈這來了 彈這來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈到這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 胸大更容易累
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸小的傢伙是不會理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『手裡劍』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來差不多是極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機票
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有機可乘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分出勝負了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認輸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機票？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德國…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 眼鏡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝飾用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種設定不需要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的 我的德國旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『88(FLAK36 88毫米炮)』
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擋不住的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一發
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉 做過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是失去理智 才是最危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 好像是我把機票弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉小姐本來不是妖怪的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 小的時候因作亂的妖怪而被侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成了一半人類一半妖怪的半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多人被侵蝕以後會失去自我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然也會有保持清醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因為那傢伙很堅強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『樹』
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在變稀薄呢  『七鄉』
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我討厭被約束啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了就好了 贏了的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉OK大會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優勝獎品德國旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳相信命運的紅線嗎？相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好偶然哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然？不對 這是必然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.81,0:09:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是言葉的話 我覺得肯定會勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前有要做的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}補習參加者 \N五十音言葉\N以上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的專長是德語啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不明白英文 也不會困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}在校門口等妳哦\N卡拉OK的預約已經辦好了\N立即開始特訓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有年輪蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有德國香腸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能喝啤酒就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs20}這三樣都是德國的名物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有名嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想獲勝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是言葉的話 肯定會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…是認識的吧 和那個半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加工橡膠 樹脂類 酸化亞鉛以及其他的物質\N將這些物質提煉而成為一種具有粘性物質\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平均的伸展在布料上製成 在正中央依附上紗布\N單手也可以進行治療的醫療物品…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 但是普通說聲『OK繃』 出不來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像牆壁 冰之類的簡單物質可以直接顯現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言靈也不是萬能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是蠻不便的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那個孩子就是半妖啊 ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的普通吶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像人類一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼名字來著…那個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要邊唱歌邊練習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要在卡拉OK大會上取得優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然天空的有著很高的距離感(町歌)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:12:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是朝向遼闊的空中…飛去吧(町歌)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用這首歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹭蹭 得累 蹭得累 蹭蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹭蹭 得累 蹭得累 蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道她們先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那位半妖小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（不曉得的他在唱蝦米東東）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 那個是什麼啊 歌曲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是歌曲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是朗讀一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像說唱一樣不是很帥氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道言葉去哪裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了仍然沒有到事務所來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙偷懶去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也打過電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是在練習卡拉OK的歌曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙也是…那個傢伙也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有把我也給加進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接通了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 現在有要事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的可真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個男人的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心…沒死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向她們打聽到了許多關於妳的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一直在哭鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就讓她們稍微的睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然對我的朋友出手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是向她們打聽了一點事情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『Maschinenpistole(衝鋒鎗)』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈…』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『棒』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們非要相互爭鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同為被侵蝕之人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵蝕？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.57,0:14:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和妳都是被妖怪選中的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.44,0:15:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『手榴彈』
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是強勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是正是因為這種力量而被人類所討厭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『Maschinenpistole(衝鋒鎗)』
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也應該是明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪和人類是不肯能在一起生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『斧頭 斧頭 斧頭 斧頭 斧頭…』
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉強自己阿諛奉承 裝作和一般人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是人類卻不把妳當作同類 討厭妳 憎恨妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳今後依舊也要生活在這種世界中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是一座偽善的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:17:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說 這個世界是痛苦的 難道不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就讓我們來製造原本屬於我們的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這雙手…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我不知道那種理論
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照自己的想法去做就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墜落之時的妖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不屬於人類 是和我們一樣的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對…不對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對…不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉 不要忘記那天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是隔壁班的五十音言葉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是人類 名字是言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記了那麼簡單的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了 那個就是我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真是會給我添麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…正在興頭上的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是円神的手下？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就來作為妳的對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『彈彈彈彈彈彈…』
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『彈彈彈彈彈彈…』
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白費力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『88(FLAK36 88毫米炮)』
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:19:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起 都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在全力戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個去練歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都預約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德國
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要取得優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.99,0:20:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麥克風
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡唱歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了這個就可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音…聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲……聲音啞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:20:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是我會贏…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 不肯能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 德國
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的德國啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.73,0:22:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}幹勁十足的女子高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.73,0:22:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出錢來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.12,0:22:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉好厲害 能幹的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.42,0:22:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被欺騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.12,0:22:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拆穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.79,0:23:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便浪費言靈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.36,0:23:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}戰鬥中的女子高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.35,0:23:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『Maschinenpistole(衝鋒鎗)』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.33,0:23:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.97,0:23:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能幹 真能幹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.75,0:23:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  加油  言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.20,0:23:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.95,0:23:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬到舌頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不頂用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.33,0:23:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}學習中的女子高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫習書本
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.62,0:23:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正安時代（正安 日本鐮倉末期的年號）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.56,0:23:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約至今1250年
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉看上去好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨近考試了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.97,0:23:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.43,0:23:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖德太子 聖德太子跑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快讓他回去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.39,0:23:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提問 我會變出什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.33,0:23:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直徑十毫米圓型的物體
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.26,0:24:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將石灰 石鹼和炭酸鈉經高溫融化做成的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.15,0:24:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又或者使用合成樹脂…
